author: scottwilson
msg: This changeset updates Wookie to provide an API that more closely matches the official W3C Widgets: API Specification.
This includes separating metadata and preferences, adding read-only preferences, and a major overhaul of injected javascript to support prototype getters and setters.
The widget used for testing the API has also been updated.

author: scottwilson
msg: replaced all Phil's code of unclear origin with generic code based on public how-to examples. A lot of the imported code from RELOAD turns out isn't used anywhere and has simply been deleted.
